  "body": "looks like --datadir is completely ignored and client keeps creating $HOME/.local/share/erigon folder for data instead of using --datdir to specificly set it elsewhere\r\n\r\n```\r\n[Unit]\r\nDescription=Erigon client\r\nWants=network-online.target\r\nAfter=network.target network-online.target\r\n\r\n[Service]\r\nUser=erigon\r\nGroup=erigon\r\nLimitNOFILE=16368\r\nEnvironment=HOME=/opt/erigon\r\nType=simple\r\nExecStart=/opt/erigon/erigon \\\r\n--chain bsc \\\r\n--port 30403 \\\r\n--http.port 8565 \\\r\n--http.api engine,erigon,net,debug,trace,txpool,shh \\\r\n--db.pagesize 16k \\\r\n--prune hrtc \\\r\n--datadir /opt/erigon/storage \\\r\n--private.api.addr localhost:9090 \\\r\n--http.addr 0.0.0.0 \\\r\n--ws \\\r\n--http\r\n\r\nKillMode=process\r\nKillSignal=SIGTERM\r\nTimeoutStopSec=90\r\nRestart=on-failure\r\nRestartSec=10s\r\n\r\n[Install]\r\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\r\n```",
